OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSocial care crisis: Woman, 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F92, waited four months to  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbe discharged              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Just a week after being admitted to    
OL,6, hospital with an infection, 92-year-old
OL,7, Esme Hanson was well enough to go home.
OL,9,FHowever it would be four months before 
OL,10,Fshe could return to her family, because
OL,11,Fof a lack of available care.           
OL,13,FOne care provider told BBC Wales staff 
OL,14,Fshortages were so bad, it handed care  
OL,15,Fpackages back to the local council.    
OL,17,FThe Welsh government said the situation
OL,18,Fis "fragile" and that it has committed 
OL,19,F#48m of extra funding to ease the      
OL,20,Fsocial care crisis in Wales.           
